N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4820.41 - Purchase of bingo supplies

State Regulations

No authorized organization licensed to conduct bingo
shall purchase or receive any bingo supplies or equipment from other than a
licensed supplier or another authorized organization. Notes
